entries.femaleVariant: If I hadn't come, you'd be cruisin' Night City in sexy wheels right now.
Unlikely it woulda worked anyway.
Nah, all my fault.
Nah, it was all my fault.
Nah, c'mon. Job was toxic from the start.
Wait, what?
Pigs didn't waddle in outta nowhere. My tech musta triggered the alarm.
Even Kabuki under-the-counter magic can't get around an alarm like that. Shoulda known I'd have the PD on my ass.
So, maybe now, as God ordained.
Jackie Welles.
V.
I know you… You hang at the Coyote.
Mhm, Coyote's where I got this job, in fact.
Wait, Welles…? Like Mama Welles? Thought I recognized the name.
entries.maleVariant: Wait, Welles... like Mama Welles. Heh, thought I recognized the name.

entries.femaleVariant: Got the job to steal those wheels at the Coyote. From Kirk.
Welles? Name's familiar.
She's my blood, all right. Coyote's her dive.
It's strange you and I never met before.
You work with that sewer slug?
Pepe owes him big and can’t afford to pay, so I stepped up.
Man, gotta wonder about Pepe, lettin' slimy Kirk boss him around like that.
Heard what they say – he's backed by cartels.
Cartels? No, no, listen, I know those cartel types, and I guarantee you none of 'em have even heard of Kirk.
C'mon, let's go have some lunch.
We buddies all of a sudden?
Lunch?
Just like that? You put a barrel to my skull not so long ago.
Lunch?
Gettin' one of my good feelings.
You help my homies, you're OK in my book. No harm, no foul?
None at all.
'Bout what?
'Bout us. Sense a kind of chemistry, y'know?
C'mon. I'm fuckin' starved.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="El cabrón" b="" a="'s gotta learn... he don't do people in Heywood dirty."/>
Haha, you would not believe my mama's chili – best in town.
Stints wouldn't do that.
Honestly, for a sec there, things looked iffy. Wasn't sure we'd worm outta that alive.
Nah, Stints wouldn't do us like that.
Man, same. Stints is out to get people, wound tight. Though, he does have a little honor left.
Same here.
You sure about that?
Uh-huh. He's Heywood-born, bred and grown like us. Hates suits as much as you do.
entries.maleVariant: Mhm. He's Heywood-born, bred and grown like us. Hates suits as much as you do.

entries.femaleVariant: Did what he had to do, that's it.
Really think his sense of honor saved us?
Well… and the fact he's Heywood-born and bred like us.
[Get up] Let's get movin'.
C'mon, no fear. Trust me.
Ready to mosey?
OK, food it is. Let's go.
Motherfucker… Agh!
